# ============================================================
# MapU .gitignore
# ============================================================

# ----------------------------------------------------------
# PROPRIETARY PROCESS & ENGINEERING WORKFLOW (NEVER PUBLIC)
# ----------------------------------------------------------

# Claude Code project instructions & agent configuration
.claude/
CLAUDE.md
**/CLAUDE.md

# Internal process documentation & engineering methodology
.process/
**/.process/

# Code review artifacts (any reviewer tooling)
**/codex_*
**/review_*
**/*_review.md
**/*_review.txt
**/*_audit.md
**/*_comparative_analysis.md

# Internal decision logs that expose methodology
**/DECISIONS_INTERNAL.md
**/ASSUMPTIONS_INTERNAL.md

# Session transcripts & agent conversation logs
**/*.session
**/*.session.json
**/sessions/

# ----------------------------------------------------------
# STANDARD PYTHON
# ----------------------------------------------------------

__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class
*.so
*.egg-info/
*.egg
dist/
build/
*.whl
.eggs/

# Virtual environments
.venv/
venv/
env/
ENV/

# ----------------------------------------------------------
# IDE & EDITOR
# ----------------------------------------------------------

.vscode/
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# ----------------------------------------------------------
# ENVIRONMENT & SECRETS
# ----------------------------------------------------------

.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.pem
*.key
*.cert
credentials.json
secrets.yaml

# ----------------------------------------------------------
# DATABASE & LOCAL STATE
# ----------------------------------------------------------

*.sqlite3
*.db
*.db-journal
*.db-wal
*.db-shm
.mapu/

